t-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">To get there:<\/strong> Take bus C30\/32 from the city for 1.40 EUR (1.42 USD). It&#x2019;s a 10-minute ride from here. You can walk to the palace if you prefer, which is a 30-minute uphill walk.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/86192&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05100758\/to-do-granada-spain-5.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05100758\/to-do-granada-spain-5-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05100758\/to-do-granada-spain-5-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Granada, Spain: Best Things To Do (Travel Guide)\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-catedral-de-granada\">2. Catedral de Granada<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Catedral de Granada sits in the center and is one of the most beautiful buildings in the city. Like many of the cathedrals in Spain, it was built on top of a mosque after the period of &#x2018;Reconquista&#x2019; (when the Christians took back <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spain<\/a> from the Moors). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12.jpg\" alt=\"Catedral de granada\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Catedral de granada\" class=\"wp-image-86864 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1356px) 100vw, 1356px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12.jpg 1356w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-424x600.jpg 424w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-572x810.jpg 572w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-239x338.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-542x768.jpg 542w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-723x1024.jpg 723w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-763x1080.jpg 763w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-1017x1440.jpg 1017w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-300x425.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-600x850.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-150x212.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These days, you can see the renaissance architectural style. This gives the Catedral de Granada an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italian<\/a> feel, especially with the beautiful marbled square in front.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>To escape the heat, visit the beautiful interior with its gold leafing, stained glass, and impressive stone arches and columns. On your way out, look for the artists painting in the outside square.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13.jpg\" alt=\"things to do granada spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do granada spain\" class=\"wp-image-86866 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03105737\/granada-spain-13.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>Entry Fee and Opening Times<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Tickets cost 5 EUR (5.50 USD), and you can do an audio tour in many languages (for no additional cost). Conveniently, you can listen on your phone by scanning a QR code as you enter. Buy your tickets at the office by the cathedral or online in advance.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Opening Times<\/strong>: 10 AM &#x2013; 6.15 PM Monday to Saturday (Sundays 3 PM &#x2013; 6.15 PM).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9.jpg\" alt=\"things to do granada Catedral spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do granada Catedral spain\" class=\"wp-image-86861 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102956\/granada-spain-9.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-mercado-la-alcaiceria\">3. Mercado La Alcaicer&#xED;a<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Just around the corner from the cathedral, discover the treasure of Mercado La Alcaiceria (a top thing to do in Granada!). Narrow alleyways are a common sight in Granada, but this is one with a difference. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class