bars and restaurants down by the riverside that have a view of Alhambra. Enjoy a drink here, especially in the early evening when the buildings turn a shade of dusky pink. You can also walk down to the river and paddle if you want to cool down from the heat! You&#x2019;ll feel a real hippy vibe in this area, with lots of people sitting enjoying nature and drinks together.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/granada-hotels\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Granada.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04121309\/granada-spain-32.jpg\" alt=\"river granada spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"river granada spain\" class=\"wp-image-86930 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04121309\/granada-spain-32.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04121309\/granada-spain-32-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04121309\/granada-spain-32-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04121309\/granada-spain-32-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04121309\/granada-spain-32-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/stat