735,15z\/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0x708fff5a5837e574?sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj9tfP2q4z5AhWJgv0HHQfIAvAQ_BJ6BAhXEAU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ermita de San Miguel Alto<\/a> (the highest viewpoint in Granada, Spain). Alternatively, for less of a walk, wander up the steps into Albaic&#xED;n center and find some of these viewpoints: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/place\/Mirador+de+San+Nicol%C3%A1s\/@37.1848999,-3.5876735,15z\/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0xd71fcc7c9e8cf95:0x59be6c3e219b6498!8m2!3d37.1811058!4d-3.5926637\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Mirador de San Nicol&#xE1;s<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/D6Tag7yN5pWpZvJRA\">Mirador Placeta de Carvajales<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6.jpg\" alt=\"things to do granada spain Albaic&#xED;n\"><\/noscript><img width=\"247\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do granada spain Albaic&#xED;n\" class=\"wp-image-86848 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1404px) 100vw, 1404px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6.jpg 1404w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6-439x600.jpg 439w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6-592x810.jpg 592w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6-247x338.jpg 247w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02155813\/granada-spain-6-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/w