x2019;s a tranquil village, home to local people (mainly the elderly), and is full of white houses and hundreds of flower pots. It&#x2019;s also one of the most beautiful villages in the region and a must-see on your Andalusia road trip!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36.jpg\" alt=\"things to do granada spain day trip iznajar\"><\/noscript><img width=\"237\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do granada spain day trip iznajar\" class=\"wp-image-86988 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1347px) 100vw, 1347px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36.jpg 1347w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-421x600.jpg 421w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-568x810.jpg 568w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-237x338.jpg 237w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-114x163.jpg 114w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-126x180.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-539x768.jpg 539w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-718x1024.jpg 718w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-758x1080.jpg 758w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/05092319\/granada-spain-36-1010x1440.jpg 1010w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\